message.entry:
Data is in MESHGRID format, NDGRID format is required.
Convert your data as follows:
 P = [2 1 3];
 X = permute(X, P);
 Y = permute(Y, P);
 Z = permute(Z, P);
 V = permute(V, P);
 F = griddedInterpolant(X,Y,Z,V)

Query data is in MESHGRID format, NDGRID format will yield better performance.
Convert your query data (Xq, Yq) as follows:
 F = griddedInterpolant(. . .);
 Xq = Xq'; Yq = Yq';
 Vq = F(Xq,Yq);

Query data is in MESHGRID format, NDGRID format will yield better performance.
Convert your query data (Xq, Yq, Zq) as follows:
 F = griddedInterpolant(. . .);
 P = [2 1 3];
 Xq = permute(Xq, P);
 Yq = permute(Yq, P);
 Zq = permute(Zq, P);
 Vq = F(Xq,Yq,Zq);
